\c 18 Hezekia mambo waJudha 1 Zvino negore rechitatu raHoshea mwanakomana waEra mambo weIsiraeri, Hezekia mwanakornana waAhazi mambo waJudha wakatanga ushe. 2 Akatanga kubata ushe ava namakore ana makumi maviri namashanu; akabata ushe paJerusaremu makore makumi maviri namapfumbamwe; zita ramai vake rakanga riri Abhi mukunda waZekariya. 3 Akaita zvakarurama pamberi paJehovha, sezvakaita baba vake Dhavhidhi. 4 Akabvisa matunhu akakwirira, akaputsa shongwe, akaparadza matanda okunamata nawo; akaputsa-putsa nyoka yendarira yakanga yakaitwa naMosesi; nokuti kusvikira pamazuva iwayo vana veIsiraeri vaiipisira zvinonhuwira, akaitumidza Nehushitani. 5 Akatenda kuna Jehovha Mwari weIsiraeri; naizvozvo hakuna wakanga akafanana naye pakati pamadzimarnbo ose aJudha, kuna vakamutevera, kana vakamutangira. 6 Nokuti wakanamatira Jehovha, haana kutsauka pakumutevera, asi wakache- ngeta mirairo yake, yakarairwa Mosesi naJehovha. 7 Jehovha akava naye; kwose kwaakaenda wakafambiswa zvakanaka;
